		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Obviously, graphical issues are the most common complaints right now with this product.  Bunnyboy warned on his site of "occasional" graphical distortions, but I don't think he realized how serious they can be (seems to vary from console to console).
<br />
<br />The fact that the problem is console-dependent tells me that it's more likely hardware than software.

		

		</td>
